WEBVTT

1
00:00:16.070 --> 00:00:18.401
<font color=#FF0000>STAR WARS
"THE CLONE WARS"</font>

2
00:00:18.758 --> 00:00:21.476
<font color=#FF00FF>*STAR WARS THE CLONE WARS*</font>
<font color=#00FF00>Season 07  Episode 12</font>

3
00:00:21.946 --> 00:00:24.149
Aired on:
<font color=#00ffff>May 04. 2020</font>

4
00:00:30.232 --> 00:00:34.000
Episode Title:
<font color=#FFc30f>"Victory and Death"</font>

5
00:00:34.085 --> 00:00:36.109
<font color=#ffc30f>Sync corrections</font> by <font color=#00FF00>srjanapala</font>

6
00:00:53.899 --> 00:00:55.474
How are we gonna
get out of here?

7
00:00:55.689 --> 00:00:57.204
I have an idea.

8
00:00:57.396 --> 00:00:58.630
Which is?

9
00:00:59.146 --> 00:01:00.935
Just set those things
to stun.

10
00:01:01.020 --> 00:01:02.623
We're not trying
to kill anyone.

11
00:01:02.796 --> 00:01:04.349
Yeah. well.
tell that to them.

12
00:01:06.380 --> 00:01:07.966
They're almost through.

13
00:01:08.218 --> 00:01:09.466
Wait.

14
00:01:10.816 --> 00:01:11.966
Wait.

15
00:01:13.200 --> 00:01:14.228
Now!

16
00:01:30.722 --> 00:01:33.044
R7.
find us a path out of here.

17
00:01:47.943 --> 00:01:50.130
All right.
Now what?

18
00:01:51.899 --> 00:01:53.708
The escape pods
have been destroyed.

19
00:01:53.793 --> 00:01:55.755
Taking a shuttle
is our best bet.

20
00:01:59.224 --> 00:02:00.443
Exhales deeply

21
00:02:00.665 --> 00:02:02.724
The boys are having
a rough time of it.

22
00:02:03.192 --> 00:02:05.061
Did you hear
Maul also escaped?

23
00:02:05.146 --> 00:02:07.372
He didn't escape.
I let him out.

24
00:02:07.646 --> 00:02:09.397
What? Why?

25
00:02:09.482 --> 00:02:11.096
Diversion.
Come on!

26
00:02:11.710 --> 00:02:13.310
That's one word
for it.

27
00:02:14.568 --> 00:02:16.693
<i>Target number</i>
<i>one's escaped the medical bay.</i>

28
00:02:16.786 --> 00:02:17.923
<i>We're in pursuit.</i>

29
00:02:18.008 --> 00:02:20.968
<i>What is the status of CT-7567?</i>

30
00:02:21.053 --> 00:02:23.480
<i>Commander Rex</i>
<i>is still missing in action. sir.</i>

31
00:02:23.564 --> 00:02:25.240
<i>Did he aid
in Tano's escape?</i>

32
00:02:25.325 --> 00:02:26.685
<i>Unknown
at present.</i>

33
00:02:44.732 --> 00:02:46.771
Target number two
is in the hyperdrive room!

34
00:03:19.130 --> 00:03:21.466
Sir. the hyperdrive generators
are failing!

35
00:03:22.281 --> 00:03:23.541
Disengage!
Disengage!

36
00:03:23.935 --> 00:03:25.435
It's too late!

37
00:04:03.757 --> 00:04:05.687
Oh. I don't like
the sound of that.

38
00:04:11.750 --> 00:04:13.606
Hangar bay
doors are sealed.

39
00:04:14.078 --> 00:04:15.599
They've got
everything locked down.

40
00:04:16.054 --> 00:04:18.624
If they weren't trying to kill us.
I'd be proud.

41
00:04:19.088 --> 00:04:21.532
R7. start unlocking the doors
on bay 12.

42
00:04:22.414 --> 00:04:24.414
Cheep. prep the shuttle.

43
00:04:24.546 --> 00:04:26.382
G-G. find out
what happened to the ship.

44
00:04:30.259 --> 00:04:31.474
- Watch it!
- Look out!

45
00:04:39.208 --> 00:04:41.178
<i>Control failed to report in.</i>

46
00:04:41.263 --> 00:04:42.445
<i>We think
they'll make their move</i>

47
00:04:42.530 --> 00:04:43.986
<i>to escape via
the main hangar.</i>

48
00:04:44.094 --> 00:04:47.812
<i>Affirmative. I want</i>
<i>squads marshaled at position 2-5 and 2-7.</i>

49
00:04:47.968 --> 00:04:49.658
<i>Wait for my signal
before proceeding.</i>

50
00:04:49.743 --> 00:04:51.098
<i>Copy that.
Lieutenant.</i>

51
00:04:54.123 --> 00:04:56.524
What do you mean
the hyperdrive is off-line?

52
00:04:58.101 --> 00:05:00.984
Destroyed?
It's completely gone?

53
00:05:04.508 --> 00:05:07.546
We're caught
in that moon's gravitational field.

54
00:05:11.849 --> 00:05:14.640
R7.
open the main hangar doors.

55
00:05:36.916 --> 00:05:38.765
We need
to get out of here.

56
00:06:01.774 --> 00:06:03.070
Any luck
with those doors?

57
00:06:04.818 --> 00:06:05.836
And the shuttle?

58
00:06:13.702 --> 00:06:14.976
There it is.

59
00:06:19.405 --> 00:06:20.968
<i>- Go!
- I can see them there!</i>

60
00:06:21.069 --> 00:06:22.460
<i>Go. go. go!</i>

61
00:06:22.968 --> 00:06:25.164
They were waiting
for us.

62
00:06:35.975 --> 00:06:37.484
Hold your position.
men.

63
00:06:37.859 --> 00:06:40.859
If they try to leave.
they'll have to go through us.

64
00:06:41.772 --> 00:06:43.242
So what do we do?

65
00:06:43.617 --> 00:06:45.107
Fight our way
to the shuttle?

66
00:06:45.852 --> 00:06:47.265
They're too many.

67
00:06:47.850 --> 00:06:50.843
Besides.
I don't wanna hurt them.

68
00:06:51.949 --> 00:06:55.484
I hate to tell you this.
but they don't care.

69
00:06:56.287 --> 00:07:00.039
This ship is going down.
and those soldiers. my brothers.

70
00:07:00.281 --> 00:07:01.656
are willing to die

71
00:07:01.740 --> 00:07:04.679
and take you and me
along with them.

72
00:07:24.773 --> 00:07:26.859
You're a good soldier.
Rex.

73
00:07:27.318 --> 00:07:29.993
So is every one of those men
down there.

74
00:07:30.687 --> 00:07:32.617
They may be willing
to die.

75
00:07:32.890 --> 00:07:36.132
but I am not the one
who is going to kill them.

76
00:07:43.153 --> 00:07:45.375
So. we're just gonna
surrender?

77
00:07:46.170 --> 00:07:49.710
Admit defeat?
Is that it?

78
00:07:51.383 --> 00:07:52.492
No.

79
00:07:53.669 --> 00:07:56.218
Well. I don't see
any other option.

80
00:08:10.528 --> 00:08:12.156
I have an idea.

81
00:08:13.493 --> 00:08:15.601
Don't worry.
It's a good one...

82
00:08:16.100 --> 00:08:17.460
...I think.

83
00:08:18.505 --> 00:08:20.179
Can I count on
the three of you?

84
00:08:24.882 --> 00:08:26.499
Good.
I'll explain on the way.

85
00:08:34.467 --> 00:08:37.125
<i>Sir. we think</i>
<i>Maul might be headed your way. Be aware.</i>

86
00:08:37.210 --> 00:08:38.670
Hold your fire!

87
00:08:43.905 --> 00:08:45.785
Hang on.
We have Tano and the commander.

88
00:08:45.898 --> 00:08:48.117
Send all remaining troops
to my position.

89
00:08:49.984 --> 00:08:51.927
I said hold your fire.
Jesse.

90
00:08:52.101 --> 00:08:54.054
I have the situation
under control.

91
00:08:54.616 --> 00:08:56.414
You have your order.
sir.

92
00:08:56.499 --> 00:08:59.249
Now execute it
or I will!

93
00:09:00.452 --> 00:09:02.576
The order was
to execute the Jedi

94
00:09:02.661 --> 00:09:04.664
for treason against
the Republic.

95
00:09:04.843 --> 00:09:09.395
The problem is.
Ahsoka Tano is no longer a Jedi.

96
00:09:09.492 --> 00:09:11.140
Hasn't been
for some time.

97
00:09:16.786 --> 00:09:19.740
Sir.
you said yourself

98
00:09:19.825 --> 00:09:22.430
we're under special order
from Darth Sidious

99
00:09:22.515 --> 00:09:24.328
to eliminate
Ahsoka Tano

100
00:09:24.473 --> 00:09:28.211
and any other clone
who disobeys Order 66.

101
00:09:29.773 --> 00:09:32.796
Just keep him talking.
a little bit longer.

102
00:09:34.278 --> 00:09:36.868
Jesse. Jesse.
listen to me.

103
00:09:36.953 --> 00:09:38.493
We've known each other
a long time.

104
00:09:38.578 --> 00:09:40.390
If we don't get this right..

105
00:09:40.474 --> 00:09:43.593
We will be the ones
committing treason. not her

106
00:09:47.039 --> 00:09:48.281
Commander Rex.

107
00:09:48.453 --> 00:09:50.945
you're in violation
of Order 66.

108
00:09:51.124 --> 00:09:52.696
I accuse you
of treason

109
00:09:52.781 --> 00:09:54.695
against the Grand
Army of the Republic.

110
00:09:54.874 --> 00:09:56.742
You'll be demoted
in rank from commander

111
00:09:56.827 --> 00:09:58.516
and subject to
execution

112
00:09:58.601 --> 00:10:00.779
along with the traitor
Ahsoka Tano.

113
00:10:03.642 --> 00:10:04.703
Ready?

114
00:10:05.999 --> 00:10:08.477
Yeah. I didn't much like
being a commander anyway.

115
00:10:08.562 --> 00:10:11.616
Company. ready.
Aim!

116
00:10:11.726 --> 00:10:13.305
Now!

117
00:10:38.793 --> 00:10:40.226
Rex. the ship.

118
00:10:48.218 --> 00:10:50.531
You wanted
this chaos.

119
00:11:19.850 --> 00:11:20.890
Move it. Move it.

120
00:11:20.975 --> 00:11:23.312
Get these lifts activated.
Get us up there.

121
00:11:23.512 --> 00:11:24.765
Our panel's locked out.

122
00:11:26.121 --> 00:11:27.966
Fire on those droids.

123
00:11:46.160 --> 00:11:47.529
The shuttle.

124
00:12:05.943 --> 00:12:07.007
Incoming.

125
00:12:07.092 --> 00:12:09.052
Surround them!

126
00:12:27.248 --> 00:12:29.552
Can't hold them off.
Too many of them.

127
00:13:31.369 --> 00:13:32.584
Blast them.

128
00:13:40.493 --> 00:13:41.550
Hey.

129
00:13:45.240 --> 00:13:46.795
Blast those
dirty droids.

130
00:14:02.198 --> 00:14:05.797
Nothing. Nothing.
Nothing.

131
00:14:06.213 --> 00:14:08.268
Everything down here
is under maintenance.

132
00:14:11.561 --> 00:14:12.760
There!

133
00:14:19.404 --> 00:14:20.823
Get me over there.

134
00:14:53.424 --> 00:14:55.964
We've entered the atmosphere.
Fire retro-rockets.

135
00:14:56.049 --> 00:14:58.753
We've lost lateral control.
We're gonna break apart...

136
00:15:02.815 --> 00:15:04.150
Look out!

137
00:15:15.911 --> 00:15:17.126
Come on.

138
00:21:16.750 --> 00:21:19.375
<font color="#ffc30f">Sync corrections</font> by <font color=#00FF00>srjanapala</font>
